FBIS4-21881 "jptot015__l94046" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 4 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA PALESTINIAN AFFAIRS Fatah, Hamas Exchange Kidnappings Fatah, Hamas Exchange Kidnappings Tehran Reports Fatah, Hamas Kidnappings LD0404073594 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 0130 GMT 4 Apr 94 LD0404073594 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] Palestinian sources yesterday announced that Fatah and the Islamic Resistance Movement, HAMAS, have each kidnapped an active member of the other group. According to these sources, HAMAS, which opposes the trend of compromise by the PLO with the Zionist regime, kidnapped Kamal 'Abd-al-Majid in the Gaza Strip. The Fatah faction, in turn, kidnapped Khalid Hindi.
